<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Front Page</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="h-screen">
    <div class="w-full h-screen bg-zinc-100 flex ">
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-gray-200 ">
            <nav class="w-full h-14 bg-gray-200 flex justify-between items-center px-8 shadow-md">
                <!-- Logo (Optional) -->
                <div class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">MindGuard</div>

                <!-- Navigation Links -->
                <div class="flex space-x-6">
                    <a href="#About-Us" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-500 font-semibold">About Us</a>
                    <a href="/Sign-in" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-500 font-semibold">Join Us</a>
                </div>
            </nav>

            <div class="flex w-full h-[calc(100%-3.5rem)]">
                <div class="w-1/2 h-full bg-zinc-300 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <!-- Video Container -->
                    <div class="w-full h-[calc(100%-3.5rem)] flex justify-center items-center">
                        <video class="w-[100%] h-[100%] object-contain pointer-events-none" autoplay loop muted>
                            <source src="../Public/Untitled design (2).mp4" type="video/mp4">
                            Your browser does not support the video tag.
                        </video>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Button Container -->
                    <div class="w-full h-14 bg-zinc-200 flex justify-center items-center">
                        <h1 class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg">A step forward for better life</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>



                <div class="w-1/2 h-full bg-zinc-200">
                    <div class="w-full h-[calc(100%-3.5rem)] p-6 flex flex-col justify-center space-y-4">
                        <!-- Heading -->
                        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center">Why Choose MindGuard?</h1>
                    
                        <!-- Description -->
                        <h2 class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify">
                            Mental health issues such as stress, anxiety ,depression, and trauma are growing concerns worldwide. Nowadays, We fail to recognize the early warning signs or seek help due to social stigma or lack of awareness. 
                            To address this, We MindGuard offers a comprehensive mental health solution. The aim is to help individuals assess and improve their mental well-being through an interactive and self-guided approach. Logging daily moods, thoughts, and emotions to track progress over time. Through Emergency Support mechanism, anybody can ask for help, counselling, and immediate assistance, support group access, mental health reports.

                        </h2>
                        <div class="w-full h-14 bg-zinc-200 flex justify-center items-center">
                            <a href="/Sign-in" class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition">
                                Join Us Now
                            </a>
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                     
                    <div class="w-full h-14 bg-zinc-300 flex justify-center">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 bg-white/20 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <!-- Icon -->
                            <div class="w-12 h-12">
                                <img onclick="openModal()" src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/005/755/264/non_2x/call-answer-icon-symbol-green-call-icon-symbol-for-web-app-logo-vector.jpg"
                                    alt="Call Icon" class="w-full h-full object-contain rounded-full">
                            </div>
            
                            <!-- Text -->
                            <div class="flex justify-center">
                                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer" onclick="openModal()">
                                    Talk to us in need
                                </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id="alertModal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
                                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Emergency Contact</h3>
                                    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Call us at: <strong>+1234567890</strong></p>
                                    <button onclick="closeModal()" class="mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600">
                                        Close
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                            <script>
                                function openModal() {
                                    document.getElementById("alertModal").classList.remove("hidden");
                                }
                                function closeModal() {
                                    document.getElementById("alertModal").classList.add("hidden");
                                }
                            </script>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <<div id="About-Us" class="w-full min-h-screen bg-gray-200 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-6 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Societal Impact</h1>
        <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>MindGuard's Goal:</strong> Improve societal wellbeing by addressing mental health issues affecting a significant portion of the population.  
            <br><br>
            <strong>Accessible Platform:</strong> Provides a user-friendly platform for mental health assessment and improvement.  
            <br><br>
            <strong>Focus on Early Recognition:</strong> Helps individuals recognize and manage stress, anxiety, and other mental health concerns early on.  
            <br><br>
            <strong>Proactive Approach:</strong> Encourages a proactive approach to mental health, leading to a healthier, more resilient society.  
            <br><br>
            <strong>Reducing Stigma:</strong> Aims to reduce the stigma associated with mental health and encourages individuals to seek help when needed.  
            <br><br>
            <strong>Benefits:</strong>  
            - Improved mental health contributes to a better quality of life.  
            - Increases productivity.  
            - Strengthens social connections.  
            <br><br>
            <strong>Overall Impact:</strong> Contributes to the overall wellbeing of the community.  
        </p>
    </div>
    
</body>

</html>